# SinarDigital Backend API

Backend REST API untuk sistem manajemen internal perusahaan **SinarDigital**.

## ğŸ“‹ Fitur Utama

- âœ… **Authentication System** - Login/Logout dengan token
- âœ… **User Management** - Multi-role (C-Level, HRD, Staff)
- âœ… **Task Management** - Buat dan assign tugas
- âœ… **Job Recruitment** - Management lowongan dan pelamar
- âœ… **Role-based Authorization** - Permission-based access control

## ğŸ“š API Endpoints

### Authentication

- `POST /api/login` - Login user
- `POST /api/logout` - Logout user

### Users

- `GET /api/users` - Get semua users (C-Level only)
- `GET /api/users/me` - Get profile user login
- `PUT /api/users/:id/status` - Update status user

### Tasks

- `GET /api/tasks` - Get semua tasks
- `POST /api/tasks` - Buat task baru
- `PUT /api/tasks/:id` - Update task

### Jobs

- `GET /api/jobs` - Get semua jobs (public)
- `POST /api/jobs` - Buat job baru (HRD only)

### Job Applicants

- `GET /api/job-seekers` - Get semua pelamar (HRD only)
- `GET /api/jobs/:jobId/applicants` - Get pelamar by job (HRD only)
- `POST /api/job-seekers` - Apply untuk job (public)

### Reports

- `GET /api/reports/dashboard` - Get dashboard data (C-Level & HRD)

## ğŸ›¡ Authorization

### C-Level

- Manage users & company
- View reports & approve budgets

### HRD

- Manage jobs & review applicants
- View reports

### Staff

- Do assigned tasks only

